org.openimaj.image.feature.local.keypoints.quantised

Class QuantisedAffineSimulationKeypoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.feature.local.quantised.QuantisedLocalFeature<AffineSimulationKeypoint.AffineSimulationKeypointLocation>
      • org.openimaj.image.feature.local.keypoints.quantised.QuantisedAffineSimulationKeypoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureVectorProvider<IntFV>, LocalFeature<AffineSimulationKeypoint.AffineSimulationKeypointLocation,IntFV>, LocalFeatureVectorProvider<AffineSimulationKeypoint.AffineSimulationKeypointLocation,IntFV>, LocationProvider<AffineSimulationKeypoint.AffineSimulationKeypointLocation>, Readable, ReadableASCII, ReadableBinary, ReadWriteable, Writeable, WriteableASCII, WriteableBinary

    public class QuantisedAffineSimulationKeypoint
extends QuantisedLocalFeature<AffineSimulationKeypoint.AffineSimulationKeypointLocation>
    A QuantisedLocalFeature with a location described by an AffineSimulationKeypoint.AffineSimulationKeypointLocation. This can be used for representing quantised local features extracted in combination with the ASIFT algorithm.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
